name: strlen
description: Calculates the length of a string.

name: strcpy
description: Copies a string to a destination buffer.

name: strncpy
description: Copies a fixed number of bytes from a string.

name: strcat
description: Concatenates two strings.

name: strncat
description: Concatenates two strings with a size limit.

name: strcmp
description: Compares two strings.

name: strncmp
description: Compares two strings up to a fixed length.

name: strchr
description: Locates the first occurrence of a character in a string.

name: strrchr
description: Locates the last occurrence of a character in a string.

name: strstr
description: Locates a substring within a string.

name: strdup
description: Duplicates a string using malloc.

name: memcpy
description: Copies a memory area.

name: memmove
description: Copies a memory area safely (handling overlap).

name: memset
description: Fills memory with a constant byte.

name: memcmp
description: Compares two memory areas.

name: memchr
description: Scans memory for a character.

name: isdigit
description: Checks if a character is a digit (0-9).

name: isspace
description: Checks if a character is a white-space character.

name: tolower
description: Converts a character to lowercase.

name: toupper
description: Converts a character to uppercase.

name: isupper
description: Checks if a character is an uppercase letter.

name: isalpha
description: Checks if a character is an alphabetic letter.

name: atoi
description: Converts a string to an integer.

name: atol
description: Converts a string to a long integer.

name: strtol
description: Converts a string to a long integer with a specified base.

name: abs
description: Computes the absolute value of an integer.

name: labs
description: Computes the absolute value of a long integer.

name: rand
description: Generates a pseudo-random number.

name: srand
description: Seeds the pseudo-random number generator.

name: bsearch
description: Performs a binary search of a sorted array.

name: qsort
description: Sorts an array using quicksort.

name: fputs
description: Writes a string to a stream.

name: puts
description: Writes a string and a newline to stdout.

name: putchar
description: Writes a character to stdout.

name: getchar
description: Reads a character from stdin.
